<h2>Forschungen zu Paul Valéry / Recherches Valéryennes (Zeitschriftenheft)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1834'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
